          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Leave No Americans Behind Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill amends the State Department Basic Authorities Act of 1956 to eliminate the requirement that Department of State evacuation loans to private U.S. citizens or third-country nationals facing war, civil unrest, or natural disasters be reimbursable.</p>]]></text>
